f/   ( f m - m  ) divide float f by float m
f>   ( f m - flag  ) flag is true if f is greater
f>i   ( f - f  ) convert 32 bit float to integer
fabs   ( f - f  ) get absolute value of float
fill   ( s n x - )fill n bytes from s with x
fneg   ( f - f  ) reverse the sign of the float
for  [i]  ( n - ) start of a loop which runs n times
gnetif   ( - a ) LwIP netif structure for Ethernet
gtt   print tick and time
help   <filtering> print words with one line help; allow wild card <filtering>; parenthesis show ( args - results ) and precede the command; angle brackets show arguments that follow commands
here   ( - a ) return address of end of dictionary
hex   interpret all following numbers as hex
hold   ( c - ) hold a character in number sequence
i>f   ( i - f ) convert integer to 32 bit float
