show-stats   show packet stats
show-sys   show system info: clock frequencies and uptime
show-telnet   show Telnet server state and active connections
show-timer   show delta timer state and UTC tick counter
show-usb   show USB connection state and CDC line status
sign   ( m n - n ) prepend sign to number sequence if m is negative
sin   ( f -  f  ) calculate the sine of f
sp!   ( ... - ) empty the data stack
sqrt   ( f - f  ) calculate the square root of f
start   create a reference point
stop   stop recording events
strlen   ( a - c ) return length of a string
swap   ( n m - m n ) swap top two items on the data stack
tabto   (n) move ahead to line position n
tan   ( f -  f  ) calculate the tangent of f
te   print counter, compare value and list of time event actions with due dates
teakeycosts   show key hashes and clustering of teatimes table
telist   print TE todo and done list of time events
testtime   ( s ) test ticks, timeouts and time for s seconds
tickms   ( tick - ms ) convert tick to milliseconds
tn   dump out names in action name array
type   ( a n - ) output n characters starting at a
until  [i]  ( n - ) go back to the begin statement if stack is zero
variable   ( n - ) <string> give n a place to be stored at a name
while  [i]  ( n - ) conditional choice in a loop construct
words   list all words in dictionary
xor   ( n m - p ) bitwise XOR top two data stack items and leave on top
